🐾 OnlyPaws - Pet Adoption & Care Website

Welcome to OnlyPaws a pet adoption and veterinary care website where every paw has a story!
An all-in-one pet care platform for booking veterinary appointments, buying pet supplies, adopting pets, and accessing basic support—all in one place.

🌟 Features

- Pet Adoption Listing - View available pets (dogs, cats, rabbits, birds, and more) ready for adoption.  
- Google Form Integration - Easily enquire or adopt a pet through embedded Google Forms.  
- Vet & Grooming Services - Info on grooming, vaccination, and emergency services.  
- Pet Store Section - Showcases pet products for convenience.  
- Chatbot Assistant - A friendly chatbot to help visitors find answers quickly.  
- Location Map Embed - Displays the center’s physical location with Google Maps.  
- Responsive & Stylish UI - Clean layout, responsive design, and elegant styling with CSS.  

📁 Project Structure

- `index.html` – Main landing page  
- `adopt.html` – Pet adoption showcase page  
- `styles.css` – Custom CSS styles  
- `assets/` – Images for pets, icons, UI  
- `README.txt` – You're here!  

📋 Technologies Used

- HTML5 – Structure  
- CSS3 – Styling and responsiveness  
- JavaScript – Chatbot, UI interactivity  
- Google Forms – For adoption inquiries  
- Google Maps Embed API – Location visibility  
- Remixicon & Swiper.js – Icons and testimonials slider  
- Hosted into AWS s3 bucket (https://onlypaws-myfirstaws.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/index.html)

